# Project Language: English

All comments, doc comments, and documentation in this project must be written in **English**.

## Applies To

- **Rust**: `//` and `///` comments, `//!` crate/module docs, docstrings
- **Markdown**: `docs/**`, `README.md`, and any `.md` files
- **Scripts**: Comments in Python, shell, or other scripts under `scripts/`

## Examples

```rust
// ✅ GOOD
/// Runs a forward pass over the given token ids.

// ❌ BAD
/// Verilen token id'leri üzerinde ileri geçiş yapar.
```

```markdown
<!-- ✅ GOOD -->
## How Coverage Is Measured

<!-- ❌ BAD -->
## Nasıl Ölçülüyor?
```

## When Adding or Editing

- Write new comments and docs in English.
- If you find non-English text in comments or docs, translate it to English.
